    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Enclosed with this letter is a sheet of condensed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "facts concerning two supposed visitors from outer space, which is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "taken from Harold T. Wilkins book \"Flying Saucers On The Attack.\"",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Since the F. B. I. was reportedly involved in the investigation I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "would like to know if the story concerning the supposed visit is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "true, a possibility, or just plain science fiction.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "If the story is true and/or if the F. B. I. has a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "report on this case in its files, I would appreciate a copy of that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "report. If it is impossible to forward me a complete copy of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "report please send a summary of the report.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "I realize this story sounds fantastic but I would",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "appreciate a reply, since it is actually suppose to have occurred.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
